NIJE BAŠ VOLIO.</i>

13
00:01:51,411 --> 00:01:53,745
<i>JEDAN, DVA, TRI.</i>

14
00:01:55,298 --> 00:01:58,068
<i>IMAO SAM OSAM GODINA.</i>

15
00:01:58,168 --> 00:02:01,753
<i>ALI, PRIÈA ZAPRAVO POÈINJE NA DAN
